  "description": "Orca's echolocation clicks feed into Overdub's spring reverb — the tank becomes the ocean. Each click pulse is caught, stretched, and returned as the physical resonance of deep water. Overdub's tape delay catches the trailing echoes so nothing is lost. The hunt has an acoustic dimension now. The prey hears the predator before they see it.",
